data.description: Looking for a home with an open design and a great gourmet kitchen. Look no further than this stunning one story home with a three car garage. Boasting spacious rooms, high-end finishes, and plenty of natural light, this home is the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. The gourtmet kitchen includes granite counters, upgraded cabinets and SS appliances with gas cooking. Whether you're a car enthusiast or simply need the storage space of a huge garage, this home has everything you need. Did I mention the private guest suite with its own bath? Come see it today and start living the life you deserve!
